Version 1.0

Description:
This application allows users to calculate the amount each person needs to pay in a group after
dinner. Users can enter the bill amount, tip percentage the group would like to give to the server
and the number of people in the party. The application will provide the amount of money each person
needs to pay.

Users Input Required:
The bill amount (double)
The tip percentage (double)
Number of persons in the party (integer)

Application Output:
Price per person (double)
